{
  "texts": [
    "All photos from the used datasets were shrunk to (256,256), cropped, rotated, and color normalized.",
    "The standard RestNet50 was then tweaked its hyperparameters to appropriately diagnose the various grades.",
    "We compared the suggested model to some cutting-edge models.",
    "We used five different performance criteria in the comparison to evaluate the model's performance in diagnosing healthy and varied Glioma grades.",
    "Transfer learning is widely used in a variety of contexts."
  ]
}